name: Swanky 1-Bedroom Suite
description:
This achingly cool studio is in Tallinn’s creative district Telliskivi. Inspired by its neighbourhood, the studio's unique Nordic-industrial style is translated into bespoke interiors by the best local designers.

Enjoy a cozy bedroom with a premium queen bed, a fully-equipped kitchen and a spacious living room. And you’re all set with hand-picked breakfast options and free gym access.
